<br>
In addition to pickup groups, there are several up-and-coming guilds that are eyeing VS.  Before long, the rotation is going to be so large that it may just collapse.  The one thing that may save the rotation is that VS is no longer an &quot;uber level&quot; mob, and the top guilds really don't have a lot of need for him.  On the other hand, VS is necessary for the wizard epic quests, which is apparently what led to the DG/PC blowup.<br>
<br>
As for whether a pickup group would become part of the rotation, my bet is that it will depend a lot on who is leading the group.  Someone like Gorndax probably has the stature to claim a permanent spot.  Someone like Darmu would have a lot harder time getting recognized as part of the rotation. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=483.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=483.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=483.topic&start=61&stop=65>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.showMessage?topicID=501.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.showMessage?topicID=32.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=483.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.threadControl?topicID=483.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=483.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=483.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub4.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpaddi